headline: Visa to Announce Fiscal First Quarter 2025 Financial Results on January 30, 2025
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, January 08, 2025--Visa (NYSE: V) will report its fiscal first quarter 2025 financial results on Thursday, January 30, 2025. After market close, Visa will furnish the results with the Securities and Exchange Commission and post them, along with accompanying financial information, on the Visa Investor Relations website. Visa will issue a news wire alert when the earnings materials are publicly available, including a link to those documents.
